# Reproducibility Statement

This document describes how to reproduce all experiments and results presented in the paper **"LockGuard RL-X: A Governance Runtime for Real-Time Detection and Containment of Adversarial Irreversibility in Multi-Agent Financial Systems"**.

## 📋 General Information

- **Paper DOI**: [10.5281/zenodo.20436834](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20436834)
- **Repository**: https://github.com/uberlandisfiolreyes74-spec/lockguard-rl-x
- **Date**: May 29, 2026
- **Author**: Uberlandis Fiol Reyes

## 🛠️ Environment Setup

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/uberlandisfiolreyes74-spec/lockguard-rl-x.git
cd lockguard-rl-x

# 2. Create and activate environment
conda env create -f environment.yml
conda activate lockguard-rlx

# Alternative with pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
